Setting up the environment
==========================

To do a local build, some software needs to be installed. I use a
mixture of conda and pip, because some modules are only available on
PyPi and some only on bioconda.

conda create gromacs-tutorials
conda activate gromacs-tutorials
conda config --set pip_interop_enabled True
conda install --file conda-requirements.txt
pip install -r requirements.txt

Building the tutorial locally
=============================

make dirhtml

Then open _build/dirhtml/index.html in your browser
